Package com.pacman.game

Class GameLogic

java.lang.Object
com.pacman.game.GameLogic
public class GameLogic
extends java.lang.Object
Class responsible for reacting to player colliding with collectable items and ghosts. Class detects such events and take actions linked to the game logic that has to be done after them.
